title: Smash Bros .Brawl 100% Complete
description:
Smash Bros .Brawl 100% Complete

Adventure completed, max coins, every characters, stages, stickers, trophyes, galleries, hammers, masterpiece and musics unlocked!


How to use:

1. Put the SD card in your computer.

2. unpack the data.bin file on to the SD card.

You put the save file in this folder: "SD card" / private / wii / title / RSBE / data.bin

3. Put the SD card back in your Wii, and go to the "data management" option and copy the save file from your SD card on to your Wii.

4. Start the game and have fun!



This is the save for USA/NTSC region Wii:s only!
